<p class="MsoNormal"><b><u><font size="5">Component Management</font></u></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size="4">Implementing a process that 
includes an integrated configuration management and component library 
environment is a way to enable successful component development life cycle.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Component-based construction is 
made possible by the quality control, storage, advertising, and shipping tasks.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="5">Why do we need a Component Manager?</font></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in" type="disc">
  <li class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">Useful engineering concept whatever the 
  scale or complexity of the software project</font></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -.25in; margin-left: 1.0in">
